| "OK" | "Confirm payment" |
| "Yes" | "Delete account" |
| "Send" | "Send payment" |
| "Continue" | "Go to review" |
| "Submit" | "Create account" |
| "Cancel" | "Back to home" |

### RULE:
> The button label must describe WHAT WILL HAPPEN, not just confirm.
> Use verb + noun: "Send Payment", "Save Draft", "Delete Account"
> Maximum 3-4 words in the label.

